    <measure>Toxicity</measure>
    <time_frame>8 years</time_frame>
    <description>To evaluate and document toxicities from chronic administration of these drugs at the doses prescribed in this protocol in patients with recurrent or progressive medulloblastoma. These will be descriptive in nature.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
